Package: com.k1tty-xz.python3
Name: Python 3.12 roothide (kysonlol)
Version: ${PY_VER}-1
Section: Development
Priority: optional
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64e
Maintainer: kysonlol
Installed-Size: ${INSTALLED_SIZE}
Depends: firmware (>= 14.5)
Conflicts: python3, org.coolstar.python3, com.bingner.python3
Replaces: python3, org.coolstar.python3, com.bingner.python3
Description: The Python 3.12 interpreter for iOS.
 This package provides a full Python 3.12 environment, including:
 .
  * The Python 3.12 interpreter (python3, python3.12)
  * Standard library with SSL support (OpenSSL 1.1.1)
  * ctypes FFI for loading dynamic libraries
 .
 Note: pip is NOT installed by default. To install it, run:
   python3 -m ensurepip
 Originally made by k1tty-xz, compiled to roothide by kysonlol.
Icon: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/k1tty-xz/python3.12-ios-arm64/refs/heads/main/icons/icon.png
